        "text": "=🚨 *API Failure — Both Endpoints Down*\n\n❌ Primary API: Failed after 3 retries\n❌ Fallback API: Also failed\n\n📋 Error: {{ $json.error_message }}\n🕐 {{ $json.occurred_at }}\n\n🔧 *Action Required:* Check API status and investigate immediately.",
