    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Resilient API Pipeline\n\nDemonstrates robust error handling patterns.\n\nWhat happens:\n1. Polls an API every 4 hours\n2. Primary call retries 3 times automatically\n3. Validates and transforms the response\n4. Stores data in Google Sheets\n5. Checks for anomalies against thresholds\n6. If primary fails, routes to a fallback API\n7. If both fail, logs the error and alerts the team\n8. A global error trigger catches anything unexpected\n\nError handling patterns:\n- Retry with backoff (node-level)\n- Error output routing (branch on failure)\n- Fallback endpoint (redundancy)\n- Error logging (audit trail)\n- Multi-level Slack notifications",
        "width": 440,
        "height": 460,
        "color": 4
      },
      "id": "c3d2e003-0001-4000-8000-000000000013",
      "name": "Sticky Note",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [100, -80]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "### Retry and Fallback Logic\n\nPrimary API fails ->\n3 retries (2s apart) ->\nStill fails -> error output\n\nError output ->\nFormat error details ->\nFallback API call\n\nFallback succeeds ->\nRoutes back to Transform\n\nFallback also fails ->\nLog error + alert team on Slack",
        "width": 280,
        "height": 300,
        "color": 3
      },
      "id": "c3d2e003-0001-4000-8000-000000000014",
      "name": "Sticky Note1",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [640, 820]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "### Global Error Handler\n\nCatches any unhandled error\nin the entire workflow.\n\nActs as a safety net so the team\nalways gets notified, even when\nsomething unexpected breaks.",
        "width": 260,
        "height": 200,
        "color": 7
      },
      "id": "c3d2e003-0001-4000-8000-000000000015",
      "name": "Sticky Note2",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [120, 1060]
    }
